'''Queen''' is a {{2|Bosses|Boss}} found in {{2|Glory}}. She fights alongside the {{M|Torch Head Amalgam}}.
== Queen ==
{{Enemy Infobox|Queen|2}} {{Power Infobox|Chains of Binding|2}}{{Keyword Infobox|Bound|2}}
=== Pattern ===
{{Intents|Queen|2}}
The Queen's pattern depends on whether the {{M|Torch Head Amalgam}} is alive:

'''Opening (always):'''
# {{Int|Queen|Puppet Strings||2}}
# {{Int|Queen|You're Mine||2}}

'''While the Amalgam is alive:'''
: Repeats {{Int|Queen|Burn Bright for Me||2}}.

'''After the Amalgam dies:'''
: If the Queen is currently using {{Int|Queen|Burn Bright for Me||2}}, she immediately switches to {{Int|Queen|Enrage||2}}, then enters the enraged loop:
# {{Int|Queen|Off with Your Head||2}}
# {{Int|Queen|Execution||2}}
# {{Int|Queen|Enrage||2}}
# Back to {{Int|Queen|Off with Your Head||2}}
* Keep in mind that Queen will have gained 2 {{KW|Strength||2}} and that the player will likely be permanently {{KW|Vulnerable||2}} from {{Int|Queen|You're Mine||2}}, making these the actual damage amounts:
** {{Int|Queen|Off with Your Head||2}}: 7x5 / {{Asc|9|9x5||2}}
** {{Int|Queen|Execution||2}}: 25 / {{Asc|9|30||2}}

{{Clear}}

== Torch Head Amalgam ==
{{Enemy Infobox|Torch Head Amalgam|2}}

=== Pattern ===
{{Intents|Torch Head Amalgam|2}}
The Torch Head Amalgam follows a fixed sequence:
# {{Int|Torch Head Amalgam|Tackle||2}}
# {{Int|Torch Head Amalgam|Tackle||2}}
# {{Int|Torch Head Amalgam|Beam||2}}
# {{Int|Torch Head Amalgam|Weak Tackle||2}}
# {{Int|Torch Head Amalgam|Weak Tackle||2}}
# Back to {{Int|Torch Head Amalgam|Beam||2}} (repeats steps 3-5)

{{Clear}}

