== Notes ==
* After a Bound card is played, other Bound cards cannot be played that turn even with effects like {{KW|Sly||2}} or a {{P|Duplicator||2}}.
* {{KW|Transform|Transforming|2}} a Bound card during battle will remove Bound from it, allowing it to be played freely.

== Trivia ==
* The Queen is based on {{M|The Collector}}, an Act 2 boss in the original Slay the Spire.

